{"tid":1984461,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【隔離期滿】袁詠儀親筆信感謝深圳政府 踏入深圳灣憂慮一掃而空","createTime":"2020-04-22T12:54:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T08:59:13.000Z","uid":141151,"like":3,"dislike":58,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"d03bb371c908b0511d68aee15ea05ed859e730d1","tid":1984461,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T12:54:20.000Z","msg":"【隔離期滿】袁詠儀親筆信感謝深圳政府 踏入深圳灣憂慮一掃而空<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200420/L36R2MCDNITEXP4VOZ2RPLRFIM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200420%2FL36R2MCDNITEXP4VOZ2RPLRFIM%2F&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6CsIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=fe7b5cf9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200420%2FL36R2MCDNITEXP4VOZ2RPLRFIM%2F&h=88d22494\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200420/L36R2MCDNITEXP4VOZ2RPLRFIM/</a><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎全球大爆發，各國政府封關封城，禁止外出，好多人都要在家工作，惟有少數工作例外，醫護人員、邊境人員就是當中少數例外。各國醫護要承受感染風險，又要面對裝備不足等問題，壓力極大，為醫護打氣及籌款，打氣方式都是各有各做，有人選擇拍片、有人出post講幾句。早前袁詠儀（靚靚）到大陸準備復工並接受14日隔離，出關後購物癮起，買完銀包又買帽。<br />\n<br />\n靚靚在隔離期間體會好深，近日有微博網民貼出一封寫給深圳南山區政府的感謝信，下款署名竟然是袁詠儀，該感謝信字跡非常工整，信末亦有大大個簽名作實。她在信中寫道，這14日隔離期是「我袁詠儀半生難忘的日子之一了」，靚靚信中指在隔離前，對過關、搭車、做快速病毒(核酸)測試等有「一萬個擔心」，但一進入深圳灣口岸「所有擔心都沒有了」。<br />\n<br />\n她稱讚各個環節嚴謹有序，職員有耐心，花了半個小時就完成程序。感謝信透露，撰寫日期是隔離結束前一日，靚靚非常正面地讚揚：「正是有你們的堅守和認真，才距離打贏防疫之戰更近一步。」"},{"pid":"f877a7d0f0914176cd9add615297c5b2853036f5","tid":1984461,"uid":199957,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T18:26:25.000Z","msg":"奶共閪既奶共日常"},{"pid":"b48440e9ec7a0c585226aa88b15f512276f09fbc","tid":1984461,"uid":47462,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T19:44:24.000Z","msg":"等睇佢中招惹埋比佢個仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e29e0bcb118262a1cfe6693adc40074cfdd1119a","tid":1984461,"uid":219277,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T19:59:00.000Z","msg":"佢同佢老公真係奶支共屎眼奶到直腸入面D屎都奶乾奶淨"},{"pid":"92379f7e80a06b09430ad250f1fdb5595d6a97c6","tid":1984461,"uid":26770,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T20:34:18.000Z","msg":"明星足球隊班叔父好<ins>了解</ins>袁詠儀"},{"pid":"a2fe31e16468f49914562fdef957196b185ece6e","tid":1984461,"uid":19676,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b48440e9ec7a0c585226aa88b15f512276f09fbc","tid":1984461,"uid":47462,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T19:44:24.000Z","msg":"等睇佢中招惹埋比佢個仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T20:45:59.000Z","msg":"佢死唔死無所謂<br />\n想睇佢死仔"},{"pid":"74c2561d0b79bc9bd77bbf0f906d35b269730216","tid":1984461,"uid":254371,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T20:59:57.000Z","msg":"同名同姓？ <br />\n奶到咁仲唔post 上微博？<br />\n冇人知寫出黎做乜"},{"pid":"ae51f4fa6c8d9218d414b0d614e3fcc136ebcc6a","tid":1984461,"uid":18695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T21:27:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb102d0a89e623806beeb0282b547ea5748674ac","tid":1984461,"uid":128603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T21:42:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0836012f4177c00a5c4f98d7d099cac7b59e59bc","tid":1984461,"uid":256127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T21:49:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/300091\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F300091&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6CsIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=6d319789\" 